Steps to perform before building the demo
=========================================

export environment variables HOST1, HOST2 and HOST3 in an alphabetical order; for instance
> export HOST1=c3po
> export HOST2=padmee
> export HOST3=vador

Export the following variable according to the name of the name from which you plan to execute the demo:
For instance if you run from "vador" then
> export HOSTNAME2=c3po
> export HOSTNAME3=padmee

CHANGE the value of the CDMW_TUTORIAL_HOME
